    "This framework was refined iteratively, drawing on seminal works, reassessing the proposed STS design principles, and continuously improving the framework.Finally, a case study method demonstrated the practical implications of the iSTS framework.",
    "In this case study, we applied iSTS to current HCAI practices, leading to the proposal of a hierarchical HCAI (hHCAI) approach.",
    "This approach addresses the gaps in existing HCAI practices from an STS perspective, offering a structured solution for integrating sociotechnical considerations into AI-driven systems.",
    "HUMAN-CENTERED AI AND SOCIOTECHNICAL SYSTEMS APPROACHES A. Human-centered AI (HCAI)HCAI is a design philosophy and approach that prioritizes humans in designing, developing, and deploying AI-based intelligent systems.",
    "HCAI emphasizes AI being designed, developed, and used to amplify, augment, empower, and enhance human performance rather than harm and replace them [1], [2], [17]."
